\begin_layout Standard
"I'll keep that in mind," Haslush said thoughtfully.
 "I'm still not tired of living, I can assure you that much.
 Plus, I know better than anyone how disgustingly underhanded the mage guild
 can be about protecting people who really don't deserve state protection, just
 because they are useful in some way… but let's not talk about that right now.
 Do you have anything else for me?"

